[[image http://scptestwiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/seal/bigman.png style="width:100%;" link=#]]
[[div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:100%;"]]
Big man.
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/collapsible]]

**Diaghilev:** Go fuck yourself.

//(Director Diaghilev abruptly ends the phone call.)//

= **<<END LOG>>**
